title: Eggo French Toaster Sticks
source: https://fryit.co/frozen-french-toast-sticks-in-air-fryer/
tags: breakfast, kid-friendly, quick and easy
servings: 4
cook time: 6 minutes
date added: 2026-03-25
---

Preheat #air fryer{} to 400°F. Place @Eggo French Toaster Sticks{1%package} in the basket in a single layer, leaving space between them for air to circulate.

Air fry for ~{5%minutes} to ~{6%minutes} until crispy and heated through. Serve with @maple syrup{}.
